Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这个世界有两类运动项目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,个人竞技和团体竞技
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.84,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而在团体竞技当中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,有一项只能两人参与的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:33.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:35.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在广阔的沙滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.52,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只有两人互相配合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.40,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,必须选择另一个无可替代的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:01:03.94,haruka-title2,,0,0,0,,{\frz9.3\move(1460,404,1536,380)\}{\fs80}{\fad(2000,0)}遥的接球
