Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:13.89,haruka-staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}翻译：小牧朝日 大布鹿     校对：DestroyerCZ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:19.28,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本机预定将于十分钟后在那霸机场着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:23.00,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,现在时间是上午10时40分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,天气晴 气温28.9℃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:36.07,haruka-title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(415.334,900.001)}{\fs70\}{\blur1\i1}{\fad(420,370)}并不需要什么王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:32.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:33.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我来啦 冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.48,haruka-screen,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.355\pos(933.334,363.332)}{\fs55}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.48,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}PS:广告板上的是冲绳方言。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,南国的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.12,haruka-screen2,,0,0,0,,{\frz338.3\move(703.199,431.6,701.8,383.466)}{\move(903.999,758,0,0)}古宇利岛\N驾车游
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.12,haruka-screen2,,0,0,0,,{\frz263.4\move(1046,805.733,1048,759.333,28,2489)}{\fs50}{\move(874,666,0,0)}{\an7\fn@微软雅黑\c&HDB56EE&}一边驾车\N一边眺望\N美丽的海景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.11,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我想去古宇利大桥看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.28,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,看起来好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,过了桥就是沙滩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:54.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.36,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那个女生 个头好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的哦 是模特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,遥到了冲绳之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,立刻打电话给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉只能让你一个人出国工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟我不会英语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不要给别人添麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,对了 你的表妹彼方也在奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,还记得她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:36.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 难道是和妈妈走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那个 你是大空遥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我是比嘉彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你是彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们最后一次见面是在四年级时的暑假对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你看 这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那时我和你差不多一样高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.40,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我以为现在应该也一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:30.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,对了 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,听说我要和彼方住同一个房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你地方变窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.32,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我房间还蛮大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这种距离感怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明今后还要住在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好担心将来的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.30,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没有海边的腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且完全没有一丝海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,为什么 好神奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 怎么回事 好厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,为什么没有海浪呢 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,水是透明的 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,游泳 冲浪 潜水都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,家的附近就有这样的海滩 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:51.87,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦 小遥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:57.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,啊呀啊呀 这么着急吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.66,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我有点担心她 所以换身衣服后就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,也是 去玩得开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.64,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美曾经练习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像至今还有人使用一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.54,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,忘记防晒 忘记防晒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本来一到这里就该涂防晒霜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,喂 那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.11,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,上面 球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.40,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:19.73,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我可以看一看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好强的压迫力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.46,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样打可以打得更高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在沙滩排球里上手托球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,更容易被判犯规哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吧 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彩纱说可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫大空遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:32.86,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,是高二生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们是同龄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我叫立花彩纱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:41.50,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,她是和我一起组队的 远井成美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:42.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我今天才刚搬来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.72,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以后要住在表妹的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你们两位是冲绳本地人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不 我来自京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不过成美很久之前就住在这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.00,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你来发球可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我托球给你之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:13.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,按刚才教你的方法试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,知道了 我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,跳得好高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本来还以为能打得更远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,脚陷在沙子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,作为第一次来说 球线飞得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:48.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,说不定未来的王牌就在现在诞生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,说的有点过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.37,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.36,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.22,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,麻烦你不要把王牌这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这么轻易地挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.53,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球是两个人的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球里不需要什么「王牌」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我是不是说了什么不该说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 她今天第一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,算了 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你们两人认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这个场地非常干净
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,就好像至今还有人使用一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:08.61,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那为什么你在那个时候没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要不要打一场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,七分制比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.58,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只要大空这边得到一分就算你们赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:41.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.86,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣 我想打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吧 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,哪边开球都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吗 那让我们来发球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 我燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:15.14,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那个 难道说规则之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没关系 我很擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.46,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,排球也在体育课上打过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大概差不多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那么 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.19,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,刚刚是因为风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,现在刚好是海风吹得最猛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我没有考虑风的因素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不过也有反过来利用风的技术哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球受风的影响很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以每七分就要交换一次场地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.44,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你有打过沙滩排球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以前打过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但你懂得好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.48,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.73,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你终于肯看着我和我说话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,因为要打比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以不得不向你做最低程度的说明而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,即便如此我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,差不多可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.32,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.07,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,正中央的高球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话我也能够…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不小心发出了奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,对不起 让你脸着地了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:20.20,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,接下来我会注意前后左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.20,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,她较真了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,现在到赛点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,轨迹和最初那球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.43,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话就不会刺到眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.07,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.52,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,屁股摔成两瓣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一开始就是两瓣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这下你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,必须要两个人才能把球打回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不管少了其中哪一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,都无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只有两人并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们才能立于球场之上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以 沙滩排球不需要王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.30,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,虽然今天我的实力还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但既然如此 我会多多练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,因为很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要是练熟了的话 一定会更好玩对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:30.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们再来一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等小遥 不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.50,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.22,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但是我有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:48.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不是现在比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:49.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:51.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一周之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:55.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,如果那时你能把规则记住 认真进行基础训练的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:58.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,再和你打一次也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了 我会认真练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.53,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等小遥 这两个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.79,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,规则的话彼方也会好好教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那我们约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.72,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 我要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我的斗志在熊熊燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,下次一定要打败你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}要做基础训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.12,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什么 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那两个人原来是高中生冠军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:50.70,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 她们是京都强校的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我呀 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.17,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我本打算告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但感觉你没打算听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但要是知道了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你就不会夸下复仇的海口了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不 就算知道也还是会试着去挑战她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 一分总能拿到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.97,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我对自己的运动神经还蛮有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 明天开始要特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:19.96,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.96,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你哼什么呢 彼方也要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,反正是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.44,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你刚才怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,感觉你刚才对初学者发了好大的脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且连复仇战都接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只要打上一周她就能明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.17,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明白什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.54,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,比如让比嘉同学借这个机会回来什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,和这件事没有关系 对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明说了今天是小遥的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,爷爷却去参加什么町内会的聚会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,竟然做了这么多菜来招待我 太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这些全都是冲绳料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 都是奶奶亲手做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.02,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这个是豆腐炒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.43,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我妈妈最喜欢吃这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.12,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是姐妹 连喜好都一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以前也很喜欢这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:41.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,冲绳猪肉味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,冲绳的节日料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,今天做了不少运动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.14,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,感觉能比平时多吃一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 沙滩排球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 真的很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我还打得很烂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:10.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我说奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:11.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方以前打过沙滩排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,现在不打了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,现在暂时…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:37.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以小遥能到这边来 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一定要和那孩子好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,收拾行李就慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:00.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,它是龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不会咬人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:05.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,它是个乖巧的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,对吧 龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:15.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我也能摸摸它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:18.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:20.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.87,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,难道我被嫌弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:35.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:37.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:39.19,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明我们今天才见面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.37,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}龟吉 让我看看嘛 让我摸摸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:44.55,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空遥 冲绳生活从今天开始了
